        <div class="pf-sign"><div><strong>Hot water takes more than 45 minutes to reheat</strong><p>A failing immersion element, corroded heat exchanger coil or faulty thermostat. We diagnose the cause and assess whether element replacement or full cylinder replacement is the right call.</p></div></div>
