        <div class="pf-sign"><div><strong>Banging or kettling from the cylinder or pipework</strong><p>Limescale on the immersion element or heat exchanger, or air in the system. Common in WA10 properties where water hardness accelerates limescale build-up. Often resolved with element replacement.</p></div></div>
